fg_segments: We respect your privacy! Any and all information collected at IMSDb will be kept strictly confidential and will not be sold, reused, rented, loaned, or otherwise disclosed.
Any information you give to IMSDb will be held with the utmost care, and will not be used in ways that you have not consented to.
A more detailed explanation about how we safeguard your personal information is described below.
If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to let us know.
IMSDb does not sell, rent, loan, trade, or lease any personal information collected at our site, including membership forms or email lists.
Our website logs are not personally identifiable, and we make no attempt to link them with the individuals that actually browse the site.
We allow third-party companies to serve adverts and/or collect certain anonymous information when you visit IMSDb.
These companies may use non-personally identifiable information during your visits in order to provide advertisements about goods and services likely to be of greater interest to you.
These companies typically use a cookie or third party web beacon to collect this information.
To learn more about this behavioral advertising practice or to opt-out of this type of advertising, you can visit networkadvertising.org.
We do not sell, rent, loan, trade, or lease the addresses on our list to anyone.

raw_html:
Privacy Policy

We respect your privacy! Any and all information collected at IMSDb will be 
  kept strictly confidential and will not be sold, reused, rented, loaned, or 
  otherwise disclosed. Any information you give to IMSDb will be held with the 
  utmost care, and will not be used in ways that you have not consented to. A 
  more detailed explanation about how we safeguard your personal information is 
  described below. If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to let us 
  know. 
 

Resale or disclosure of information to third parties:

IMSDb does not sell, rent, loan, trade, or lease any personal information collected 
  at our site, including membership forms or email lists. 

Browser information collected on the website: 

Our website logs are not personally identifiable, and we make no attempt to 
  link them with the individuals that actually browse the site. 

Use of cookies: 

We allow third-party companies to serve adverts and/or collect certain anonymous information when you visit IMSDb. These companies may use non-personally identifiable information during your visits in order to provide advertisements about goods and services likely to be of greater interest to you. These companies typically use a cookie or third party web beacon to collect this information. To learn more about this behavioral advertising practice or to opt-out of this type of advertising, you can visit networkadvertising.org.

Privacy of our email lists: 

 We do not sell, rent, loan, trade, or lease the addresses on our list to anyone.
